(:action PutObjectInReceptacle
        :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?ot - otype ?o - object ?r - receptacle)
        :precondition (and
            (atLocation ?a ?l)
            (receptacleAtLocation ?r ?l)
            (objectType ?o ?ot)
            (holds ?a ?o)
            (not (holdsAnyReceptacleObject ?a))
        )
        :effect (and
            (inReceptacle ?o ?r)
            (not (holds ?a ?o))
            (not (holdsAny ?a))
            (objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
        )
    )
